<solution>
<p><ul><li>7.22</li></ul></p><p>Because it does not matter which leg is a and which is b we call the missing leg x.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}+{4.53}^{{2}}={8.52}^{{2}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}+{20.5209}={72.5904}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}={72.5904}-{20.5209}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}={52.0695}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle\sqrt{{{x}^{{2}}}}=\sqrt{{{52.0695}}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}\approx{7.22}</m>.</p>
</solution>
